feel a little bit better.

576
00:32:41,460 --> 00:32:43,780
- Hey, John, what's up?
- Hey, George.

577
00:32:44,180 --> 00:32:47,900
I was thinking about the things
I wanted to do but haven't been able to

578
00:32:48,020 --> 00:32:50,820
and all the people that I wanted
to see, but couldn't. You know?

579
00:32:50,980 --> 00:32:53,500
Yeah.
You're feeling down, huh?

580
00:32:53,780 --> 00:32:57,620
Yeah. You could say
it's an intolerable cruelty.

581
00:32:59,380 --> 00:33:02,260
So, what kind of reaction
did you want from me on that?

582
00:33:02,380 --> 00:33:06,340
I don't know. I was hoping that you
might be able to cheer me up a bit.

583
00:33:08,740 --> 00:33:13,820
Yeah. I'm not supposed to do this,
but you seem more pathetic than usual.

584
00:33:14,100 --> 00:33:16,140
That's harsh, but also fair.

585
00:33:16,500 --> 00:33:17,940
For the next few minutes,

586
00:33:18,060 --> 00:33:22,060
I'm going to give you the power to
summon any celebrity with that snap.

587
00:33:22,340 --> 00:33:25,660
Really? George,
that is absolutely fantastic news.

588
00:33:25,740 --> 00:33:29,020
Thank you so much!
I promise I will not misuse this power.

589
00:33:29,700 --> 00:33:33,380
Yes, you will. But the beauty is,
you only have a few minutes, so, go!

590
00:33:34,100 --> 00:33:36,900
I mean, this is great!
This is so exciting!

591
00:33:37,020 --> 00:33:41,180
I feel slightly better already,
but let's not waste any time on this.

592
00:33:41,300 --> 00:33:42,860
Let's see who we get first!

593
00:33:44,340 --> 00:33:47,300
Jennifer Coolidge!
Jennifer, hi!

594
00:33:47,940 --> 00:33:49,980
Look!
It's Jimmy Kimmel!

595
00:33:50,340 --> 00:33:53,580
No, it's not. It's John.
My name's John.

596
00:33:53,660 --> 00:33:56,260
- Jimmy, I love your show.
- Thanks.

597
00:33:56,620 --> 00:33:58,380
Do you want me
to do a mean Tweet?

598
00:33:58,660 --> 00:34:03,100
- That's a different show, Jennifer.
- Is Questlove there?

599
00:34:04,140 --> 00:34:06,100
That's a different Jimmy.

600
00:34:06,620 --> 00:34:11,340
- Wait, are you the British one?
- Yes! That's me!

601
00:34:11,460 --> 00:34:13,540
I'm the British one!
Yeah, that's me!

602
00:34:14,140 --> 00:34:16,740
Do you want me
to get in a car and sing?

603
00:34:17,180 --> 00:34:18,300
For fuck's sake.

604
00:34:19,180 --> 00:34:23,180
- Hey, Will! How're you doing?
- Hey, John, what now?

605
00:34:23,500 --> 00:34:28,060
I've got a really funny story for you.
George Clooney gave me the power

606
00:34:28,140 --> 00:34:31,060
