with the snap of a finger.

607
00:34:31,140 --> 00:34:34,020
He did that again? He gives
that power away to anyone.

608
00:34:34,100 --> 00:34:37,500
Last week I got summoned by a guy
who sold Clooney a pack of Trident.

609
00:34:37,620 --> 00:34:40,220
That makes me feel significantly
less special.

610
00:34:41,180 --> 00:34:43,020
RuPaul! Hey, Ru!

611
00:34:43,180 --> 00:34:47,940
I'm sorry, my dear, but it's time
for you to sashay away.

612
00:34:48,100 --> 00:34:51,620
I'm not a contestant on your show.
It's me! It's John Oliver.

613
00:34:53,940 --> 00:34:58,860
I thought it was one of the queens
dressed up as a marionette doll.

614
00:34:59,420 --> 00:35:02,420
No, Ru.
Just me and my actual human body.

615
00:35:03,140 --> 00:35:04,220
Cute.

616
00:35:04,860 --> 00:35:07,340
I mean, that was fun.
That was definitely fun.

617
00:35:07,460 --> 00:35:09,740
But I guess there is no point
in stopping if we've still got time.

618
00:35:09,900 --> 00:35:13,540
Let's see who else we can get.
Holy shit! Cardi B!

619
00:35:13,900 --> 00:35:16,660
- Hi, Cardi!
- Who said that?

620
00:35:16,860 --> 00:35:18,700
- I'm John, but...
- Alexa?

621
00:35:18,780 --> 00:35:23,260
No, not Alexa, I'm John Oliver.
It's lovely to meet you.

622
00:35:23,420 --> 00:35:27,580
- I never thought we'd get to speak...
- Alexa? FBI?

623
00:35:27,820 --> 00:35:28,900
Forget it.

624
00:35:29,500 --> 00:35:35,860
Surprise! Listen, your little
brother Billy reached out to me

625
00:35:35,940 --> 00:35:40,060
