626
00:35:40,420 --> 00:35:44,420
This is freaking huge.
That's what she said!

627
00:35:44,620 --> 00:35:47,740
- Brian, sorry...
- Holy shit.

628
00:35:48,860 --> 00:35:51,220
No. The Cameos never talk back.

629
00:35:51,340 --> 00:35:53,260
Yeah, Brian, I think
there's been a misunderstanding,

630
00:35:53,340 --> 00:35:55,140
I didn't order a Cameo from you,

631
00:35:55,260 --> 00:35:57,740
I snapped my fingers
and now we're talking...

632
00:35:57,820 --> 00:36:01,860
John, if this isn't a Cameo,
