633
00:36:03,980 --> 00:36:06,540
Kevin from "The Office"
does not mess around.

634
00:36:06,860 --> 00:36:09,620
All right, one more push.
Here it goes!

635
00:36:10,980 --> 00:36:13,980
Cardi, it's me again.
Sorry. I'm sorry, Cardi.

636
00:36:14,180 --> 00:36:17,260
Siri, tell Alexa to stop.
Alexa, stop.

637
00:36:17,580 --> 00:36:19,380
There's nothing to stop here.

638
00:36:19,460 --> 00:36:20,900
I've got it, don't worry.

639
00:36:20,980 --> 00:36:23,020
Void!
Void, great to see you!

640
00:36:23,460 --> 00:36:26,980
Hey, John. Decent to see you, as well.
I can't really talk at the moment,

641
00:36:27,100 --> 00:36:29,620
I'm hosting my own talk show now.

642
00:36:29,900 --> 00:36:31,300
- Really?
- Yeah, kinda busy.

643
00:36:31,420 --> 00:36:32,540
That's great!

644
00:36:32,620 --> 00:36:35,180
Yeah, apparently HBO Max
liked the vibe of this space

645
00:36:35,300 --> 00:36:39,180
and they just thought it would be
better suited for a comedy show.

646
00:36:39,500 --> 00:36:43,820
- And not what you were doing.
- I get it. You're being mean to me.

647
00:36:44,620 --> 00:36:47,580
Thank goodness. Leslie,
I'm so glad it's you.

648
00:36:47,660 --> 00:36:49,380
- Nah!
- What do you mean, no?

649
00:36:49,540 --> 00:36:52,340
What are you talking about, no?
Hey, it's John. Leslie...

650
00:36:52,460 --> 00:36:54,420
I don't want this.
I don't want to be part of this.

651
00:36:54,580 --> 00:36:57,260
- Alakazam.
- Part of what? We're just talking.

652
00:36:57,380 --> 00:37:00,340
- How do I get rid of you? Go away!
- Don't clap me away!

653
00:37:00,420 --> 00:37:02,620
It's not even a clap anyway,
it's a snap!

654
00:37:02,940 --> 00:37:06,300
You've just got to snap your fingers.
Just snap your finger.

655
00:37:06,380 --> 00:37:09,420
- The white man won't leave!
- I will, I'll leave!

656
00:37:09,780 --> 00:37:11,420
Time's up! How was it, John?

657
00:37:11,660 --> 00:37:14,780
People were pretty relentlessly
mean to me, George. But honestly?

658
00:37:14,900 --> 00:37:17,140
- It was kind of great.
- I knew it would be.

659
00:37:17,220 --> 00:37:20,780
Remember, just because this year didn't
work out like you thought it would,

660
00:37:20,860 --> 00:37:24,220
that doesn't mean that shamelessly
bringing in celebrities for the finale

661
00:37:24,300 --> 00:37:25,620
wouldn't cheer you up.

662
00:37:26,140 --> 00:37:28,180
Because Say it with me!

663
00:37:29,060 --> 00:37:31,380
Celebrities make
everything better,

664
00:37:31,540 --> 00:37:35,580
except in the many situations
where they do not.

665
00:37:36,620 --> 00:37:39,060
- That's right. And hey, John.
- What?

666
00:37:39,460 --> 00:37:40,900
Goodnight and good luck.

667
00:37:41,300 --> 00:37:45,740
That's it. I do feel
20 percent better now, at least.

668
00:37:46,140 --> 00:37:48,500
Thank you so much
for watching our show this year.

669
00:37:48,620 --> 00:37:51,620
We all really appreciate it.
We'll see you next year.

670
00:37:51,700 --> 00:37:53,900
Please stay safe until then.
Goodnight!

671
00:37:54,820 --> 00:37:56,860
Do you want me to get in a car
